{"tid":1663238,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯：巴塞有人唔歡迎尼馬","createTime":"2019-10-19T09:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T06:21:02.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f275468dd8a0d6b79c715828646c85eaca2b8fa2","tid":1663238,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:45:29.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】今夏盛傳尼馬回歸巴塞隆拿，最終未有成事，美斯承認陣中不少人都不希望看到尼馬再次加盟。<br />\n<br />\n「再把尼馬（Neymar）帶回來真的很困難。」球王美斯（Lionel Messi）說。「首先，他很難才能離開巴黎聖日耳門，其次是他當年走得太醜陋了，巴塞隆拿有些人不想他回來。」<br />\n<br />\n美斯跟尼馬做過4年隊友，坦言這名27歲巴西國腳非常好波，可以幫助巴塞：「從體育的角度去看，尼馬是世界上其中一位最佳球員，但我明白需要考慮其他因素。」<br />\n<br />\n32歲的美斯最近表示，不想效力巴塞以外其他球會，希望整個球員生涯都在魯營，之後傳出他將會簽下終身合約。這阿根廷國腳澄清：「我不想被合約綁住，因為不知道自己之後想怎樣。」"},{"pid":"b5281a24d7d724f6695c8081a6dce2aa0d302288","tid":1663238,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:46:16.000Z","msg":"【1020 尖咀見】真。遊行指南參考<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/aksjJwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aksjJwU</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f47de6e53a943ac86b3d498bd91a821c2f058543","tid":1663238,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:46:34.000Z","msg":"其次是他當年走得太醜陋了，巴塞隆拿有些人不想他回來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/39c6ea4bd17b6823289ca893e117fabe/tumblr_inline_pb014x2zFp1rz5mj3_400.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F39c6ea4bd17b6823289ca893e117fabe%2Ftumblr_inline_pb014x2zFp1rz5mj3_400.gif&h=f872e70b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7936e75be8e65f8369b3c9a5cbaa3c7d9f0d82cd","tid":1663238,"uid":70439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f47de6e53a943ac86b3d498bd91a821c2f058543","tid":1663238,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTi